    "description": {
      "value": "<p>(You cannot lose concentration on this jutsu as a result of damage.) You form your chakra into a suit of armor that radiates light. For the duration, you gain the following:</p><ul><li>DR against non-psychic damage equal to your ninjutsu modifier.</li><li>Resistance to force and necrotic damage</li><li>You radiate bright light out to 30 feet, and dim light for an additional 30 feet.</li></ul><p>In addition, allied creatures, other than yourself, within 30ft of you gain the following:</p><ul><li>Resistance to force and necrotic damage</li><li>Regain 2d8 hit points at the start of each of their turns.</li></ul><pre><code></code></pre>",
